At inference, TuneJury calls the LAION-CLAP-Music encoder (CC0 1.0)
and the MERT-v1-330M encoder (CC BY-NC 4.0). Downstream users who
deploy the full scoring pipeline commercially must respect the
non-commercial constraint inherited from MERT.
